WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.200
=Episode 25=

00:00:55.759 --> 00:00:56.759
Chen,

00:00:57.679 --> 00:00:58.359
did Mr. Qin

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:00.359
really give you

00:01:00.799 --> 00:01:01.759
this house?

00:01:02.560 --> 00:01:03.000
Really.

00:01:03.719 --> 00:01:05.320
The deed has my name on it.

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:07.560
But this place is too expensive.

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:09.439
That's a huge favor to owe someone.

00:01:09.759 --> 00:01:12.400
I don't feel comfortable living here.

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:13.159
Dad,

00:01:13.599 --> 00:01:15.280
you should just relax and stay here.

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:15.959
It's fine.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:17.959
Dad, how about this?

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:19.400
Just try living

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.400
here for a while.

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:22.519
If you still feel uneasy later,

00:01:22.519 --> 00:01:24.519
we'll return it to Mr. Qin.

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:26.879
No!

00:01:27.879 --> 00:01:29.239
Absolutely not!

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:30.079
No.

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:31.000
Listen to me.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:31.800
What's there to say?

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:34.550
If anyone tries to make me move out,

00:01:34.719 --> 00:01:36.040
I'll fight them for it!

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:45.760
Changkun,

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:49.280
can you really bear to see me

00:01:49.437 --> 00:01:52.337
living in that run-down old house?

00:01:52.620 --> 00:01:53.920
You've got such a big villa here.

00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:55.959
Shouldn't you let me

00:01:55.959 --> 00:01:57.350
enjoy it first?

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:58.840
Let me move in.

00:01:59.480 --> 00:02:00.159
Mom,

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:04.680
this villa was given to Chen.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.599
I can't make that decision.

00:02:06.959 --> 00:02:08.120
You can't?

00:02:08.519 --> 00:02:10.275
He's your son-in-law.

00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:11.640
You're his father-in-law.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:13.239
If you ask,

00:02:13.799 --> 00:02:14.800
would he refuse?

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:16.280
Grandma,

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:18.719
please don't make things hard.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.900
This villa doesn't belong to us.

00:02:21.012 --> 00:02:23.280
If you want it,
you should respect Ye Chen's decision.

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:25.599
If he doesn't agree, no one can take it.

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:26.719
Insolent!

00:02:27.225 --> 00:02:28.757
Is that how you talk to me?

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.919
Where's your respect?

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:31.080
Kneel down!

00:02:33.039 --> 00:02:33.937
Respect?

00:02:35.225 --> 00:02:37.000
Respect is earned.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:39.125
What do you have

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:40.936
besides your status?

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:43.199
Ye Chen,

00:02:43.599 --> 00:02:44.879
listen up!

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.240
I'll give you one last chance.

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:48.800
You and Xiao Churan,

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:49.680
kneel and apologize

00:02:49.879 --> 00:02:50.879
right now!

00:02:51.862 --> 00:02:54.220
And hand over the villa!

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.319
Or don't blame me

00:02:56.159 --> 00:02:58.650
for being ruthless!

00:03:02.479 --> 00:03:03.360
Xiao Changkun,

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:06.039
look at your daughter

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:08.479
and your useless son-in-law!

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:10.080
Fine.

00:03:10.599 --> 00:03:11.439
If they won't kneel,

00:03:11.919 --> 00:03:13.080
you're my son,

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:14.719
you will!

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.240
The house belongs to Chen.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.240
He has the right

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.599
to accept or refuse it.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:27.479
Churan didn't say anything wrong.

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.590
She didn't do anything wrong either.

00:03:30.479 --> 00:03:31.680
Why should she kneel?

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:34.290
Please show some self-respect.

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:37.520
You've grown some backbone!

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.520
You side with outsiders

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:40.560
instead of me?

00:03:40.840 --> 00:03:43.262
You unfilial thing!

00:03:43.262 --> 00:03:45.240
You're going to anger me to death!

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:57.479
Dad.

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:58.039
Dad.

00:04:06.639 --> 00:04:07.560
I'm back.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:11.960
Just lie down and rest.

00:04:19.280 --> 00:04:20.120
We'll keep this.

00:04:20.250 --> 00:04:21.120
It can still be used.

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:24.160
What are you doing?

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.319
Don't move.

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:26.120
- I'll do it.
- No.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:26.759
Let me do it.

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:27.079
I...

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:29.680
I can't just watch you working yourself.

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:32.160
I can help with this too.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:33.879
Let me see.

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.120
Why are you so silly?

00:04:36.230 --> 00:04:37.800
You actually hit yourself with a stick.

00:04:38.079 --> 00:04:39.120
And that hard too.

00:04:42.300 --> 00:04:43.639
Honestly, I think it was worth it.

00:04:44.879 --> 00:04:46.800
That hit felt

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:48.759
pretty satisfying.

00:04:49.390 --> 00:04:50.800
Look at you, acting all tough now.

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:54.600
Just because I'm not showing my teeth

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.759
doesn't mean I'm a pushover.

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:59.480
I had to show them
I've got a temper too.

00:04:59.879 --> 00:05:01.040
I'm still a man.

00:05:02.199 --> 00:05:03.720
Why don't you show it more often?

00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:05.519
Well...

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:06.780
I'm just saving up my strength.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:08.439
Charging up for a lifetime,

00:05:09.037 --> 00:05:10.617
just to use it for two minutes?

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:15.399
What's wrong?

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:16.199
Does it hurt again?

00:05:16.439 --> 00:05:18.040
Stop joking around.

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:19.879
My head's spinning.

00:05:19.879 --> 00:05:20.560
Let me see.

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:22.519
Does it hurt?

00:05:22.519 --> 00:05:23.850
- I'll blow on it.
- Okay.

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:29.240
Still hurts?

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:29.800
No.

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:30.680
It's fine.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:31.839
Churan and Chen

00:05:32.175 --> 00:05:34.481
have really made it now.

00:05:34.879 --> 00:05:35.537
From now on,

00:05:35.937 --> 00:05:37.619
we don't have to bow to anyone.

00:05:38.300 --> 00:05:39.880
We don't have to be
afraid of anyone either.

00:05:40.319 --> 00:05:41.000
And you.

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:42.600
Don't cause any more trouble.

00:05:43.959 --> 00:05:45.480
Let's just live honestly.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:47.920
Live a good life.

00:05:48.650 --> 00:05:49.680
That'll drive them crazy.

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.160
Churan,

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:03.360
thank you.

00:06:04.639 --> 00:06:05.439
Thank me?

00:06:06.319 --> 00:06:07.199
For what?

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:09.279
For giving me a home.

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:18.279
This is outrageous!

00:06:18.279 --> 00:06:19.279
They've gone

00:06:19.279 --> 00:06:19.959
too far!

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:20.750
It's downright

00:06:20.839 --> 00:06:21.920
lawless!

00:06:22.487 --> 00:06:25.480
My villa!

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.959
I can't swallow this humiliation!

00:06:27.839 --> 00:06:29.040
Not only do we swallow it,

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:32.240
we should prepare gifts

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:34.412
and congratulate them properly.

00:06:36.439 --> 00:06:39.040
Ye Chen isn't the useless fool
he used to be.

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.720
A direct confrontation won't work.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.720
If we can't do it openly,
we'll do it quietly.

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:45.319
Don't worry.

00:06:45.320 --> 00:06:46.480
He won't live there for long.

00:06:49.275 --> 00:06:50.837
Why are you here again?

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:54.040
We came to congratulate you
on moving into your new home.

00:06:54.839 --> 00:06:55.900
Lan.

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:57.720
Ms. Lan,

00:06:58.199 --> 00:07:00.639
it was Old Mrs. Xiao
who insisted on causing trouble.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.800
We tried to stop her.

00:07:03.439 --> 00:07:04.759
Please don't take it to heart.

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:08.000
This is a gift we prepared.

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:09.680
Congratulations!

00:07:09.959 --> 00:07:10.920
Please accept it.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:11.439
Take it.

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:13.439
Changkun,

00:07:14.279 --> 00:07:17.160
we're family after all.

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:18.319
If you're doing well,

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:20.319
I'm happy for you.

00:07:20.959 --> 00:07:21.800
Exactly.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:24.120
When family stands together,
we can achieve anything.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:26.560
Harmony brings prosperity!

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:27.240
That's right.

00:07:27.519 --> 00:07:29.319
If you had been more reasonable earlier,

00:07:29.759 --> 00:07:31.160
none of this would have happened.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.160
- Yes
- You're right.

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:34.800
We're not petty people.

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:36.337
Let's just put this behind us.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:37.759
Ms. Lan.

00:07:37.959 --> 00:07:38.480
Come sit.

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.040
Take a seat.

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:39.839
Let's go inside.

00:07:39.959 --> 00:07:40.319
Okay.

00:07:40.490 --> 00:07:41.279
- Let's go.
- Here.

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:45.160
Is everything okay?

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:47.839
Are you done?

00:07:48.199 --> 00:07:49.040
Wait,

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:49.839
it's crooked.

00:07:50.150 --> 00:07:51.360
How long is this going to take?

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:52.560
Almost there.

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:54.959
You really take your time.

00:07:54.959 --> 00:07:55.600
Done.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:57.480
Mr. Ye, I'm working here, you know.

00:07:57.500 --> 00:07:58.880
Isn't that torture enough already?

00:07:59.199 --> 00:07:59.720
Take a look.

00:08:01.199 --> 00:08:02.639
Six outside, four inside.

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:05.680
Twenty-four-hour surveillance coverage.

00:08:05.879 --> 00:08:06.680
You can rest easy.

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:07.959
Good job.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:09.800
So,

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:12.360
anything else you need?

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:15.680
Have you been in touch
with Wang Dongxue lately?

00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:20.480
I can't exactly tell you that.

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:21.959
Stay away from that woman.

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:23.800
Why?

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:24.480
It's a secret.

00:08:25.839 --> 00:08:26.839
Just follow my orders.

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:27.959
It'll keep you safe.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:51.720
Mr. Qin,

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:53.000
thank you for the villa.

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:54.240
You're welcome.

00:08:55.919 --> 00:08:57.679
Could you arrange for more bodyguards

00:08:57.679 --> 00:08:58.799
to patrol the area?

00:08:58.799 --> 00:08:59.559
I'll pay for it.

00:09:00.039 --> 00:09:00.900
I'll take care of it.

00:09:02.300 --> 00:09:03.190
How's everything going?

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:04.759
Have you spoken

00:09:04.759 --> 00:09:05.360
to Tang Sihai?

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:07.440
I'm waiting a bit longer.

00:09:07.879 --> 00:09:09.399
He'll just deny everything for now.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.159
Once I uncover the truth,

00:09:11.279 --> 00:09:12.080
I'll confront him.

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:14.440
Where will you start?

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:15.080
The accounts.

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:17.559
The driver who hit Madam Li

00:09:17.559 --> 00:09:18.759
once received a payment

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.519
from an overseas account.

00:09:20.960 --> 00:09:22.600
Tang Sihai blamed you and claimed

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.039
the account couldn't be traced.

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:25.480
I plan to investigate it myself.

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:27.879
I see.

00:09:28.759 --> 00:09:30.240
We're thinking the same way.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.559
I'm also investigating

00:09:32.559 --> 00:09:34.120
the person behind Ichiro Ohara.

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:36.919
His payment came from overseas too.

00:09:37.337 --> 00:09:38.200
You might want

00:09:38.287 --> 00:09:39.559
to ask Song Wanting.

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:40.440
(Citibank Singapore and HSBC UK Bank)
Her family runs

00:09:40.799 --> 00:09:42.240
an antique auction business.

00:09:42.399 --> 00:09:43.600
That industry is complicated.

00:09:44.039 --> 00:09:45.559
A lot of dirty money

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:46.879
moves through underground banks

00:09:47.039 --> 00:09:48.639
and other gray-market channels.

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:51.100
She understands it well.

00:09:52.537 --> 00:09:54.075
(HSBC UK Bank)

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:55.290
Ms. Song, I appreciate your help.

00:09:56.960 --> 00:09:58.879
I can investigate, but it will take time.

00:09:59.879 --> 00:10:01.200
The sooner, the better. Thank you.

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:02.840
Just doing my part.

00:10:02.840 --> 00:10:04.279
Mr. Ye, I'll update you.

00:10:04.759 --> 00:10:05.159
Great.

00:10:05.799 --> 00:10:07.600
If you ever need my help,

00:10:07.759 --> 00:10:08.962
just say the word.

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.150
Old Mrs. Song, take care.

00:10:13.500 --> 00:10:14.120
I'll get going.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:14.799
Mm.

00:10:27.399 --> 00:10:29.320
Grandpa, did you see him clearly?

00:10:29.919 --> 00:10:31.360
He really is Ye Changying's son.

00:10:32.879 --> 00:10:33.900
It would be wonderful

00:10:34.639 --> 00:10:36.480
if he could work for us.

00:10:39.279 --> 00:10:40.000
What a pity.

00:10:59.799 --> 00:11:02.000
(Wang Dongxue suddenly appeared.)

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:05.960
(And Madam Li was attacked
by a mysterious assailant.)

00:11:06.550 --> 00:11:08.440
A year before your dad's accident,

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:10.120
they had a huge argument.

00:11:10.120 --> 00:11:11.919
After that, they never spoke again.

00:11:12.159 --> 00:11:13.720
The money paid to Ichiro Ohara also

00:11:14.187 --> 00:11:16.559
(Citibank Singapore and HSBC UK Bank)
came from an overseas account.

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:20.559
(Those two banks might actually be linked
to the same person.)

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:25.159
(Tang Sihai,)

00:11:25.919 --> 00:11:28.587
(are you the one
who killed my parents or not?)

00:11:47.150 --> 00:11:49.640
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:11:49.730 --> 00:11:53.480
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:11:53.940 --> 00:11:58.880
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:11:59.040 --> 00:12:01.330
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:01.640 --> 00:12:04.320
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:08.020
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:11.330
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:11.530 --> 00:12:14.580
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:14.690 --> 00:12:17.650
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:21.080
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:25.050
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:12:25.050 --> 00:12:27.920
♪I belong to no one♪

00:12:27.980 --> 00:12:31.430
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:12:31.430 --> 00:12:34.100
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:12:34.100 --> 00:12:40.440
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪